'''''Fiela's Child''''' ni ikinamico yo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika y'Epfo]] yanditswe na Dalene Matthee kandi yasohotse mu 1985<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/49458-fiela-se-kind/cast</ref>. Igitabo cyanditswe mbere muri [[Ikinyafurikansi|Afrikaans]] ku izina rya '''''Fiela se Kind''''', nyuma kiza guhindurwa mu [[Icyongereza|Cyongereza]], [[Igifaransa]], [[Ikidage]], [[Icyesipanyole|Icyesipanyoli]], igitaliyani, Igiheburayo, Isilande na Sinhalese, n'ibindi<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/49458-fiela-se-kind</ref>.

== Insanganyamatsiko ==
Matthee akemura ibibazo by’ibidukikije, insanganyamatsiko zishingiye ku ivanguramoko no kuvangura amoko. blue-buck burenze guhigwa kandi inzovu ziricwa<ref>https://bestsimilar.com/movies/51278-fielas-child</ref> . Umubano hagati y'abazungu nabandi birabura uragoye<ref>https://www.allmovie.com/movie/fielas-child-v280950/cast-crew</ref>. Nubwo ibi mbere ya Apartheid mugihe tekiniki habaye uburinganire imbere y amategeko, gahunda y'amategeko <ref>https://mubi.com/films/fiela-se-kind</ref>yabogamye kandi ishyigikira abazungu. Inganda zo mu nyanja zibabajwe no kwinjiza amato akoreshwa na parike<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fielas_child</ref>.

== Ibice byo kugarukira ==
Mu gitabo cyanditswe na Dalene Matthee icyerekezo cyo kugarukira, aho umuntu abasha guhitamo uwo ari we n'icyo agomba kuba afite, uruhare runini. Mu gitabo<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/fiela-s-child/m0bdb8j5?hl=en</ref>, Benjamini ari mu ntera ntarengwa kandi ntazi umwirondoro we. Na none, igenamiterere risobanurwa ko riri murwego ntarengwa bityo bibera kumpande zombi z'umusozi <ref>https://www.moviemeter.nl/film/96461</ref> .

== Filime ==
Igitabo cyakozwe muri firime mu 1988 gikinwamo Shaleen Surtie-Richards nka Fiela. <ref>[https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0144200/maindetails Fiela se Kind (1988)]</ref> Filime muri 2019 yakinnye na Zenobia Kloppers nka Fiela<ref>https://www.gradesaver.com/fielas-child</ref>.

